    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i just feel like i'm stuck in a loop. every time i try to \"get better\" it just falls apart and i end up making things worse for them. sometimes i look at them sleeping and i just think... if i wasn't even here, they could finally just be happy and free from all this. it almost feels like the only way to actually help them is to stop being such a burden.",
